# - Try to find GLIB2
# Once done this will define
#
#  GLIB2_FOUND - system has GLIB2
#  GLIB2_INCLUDE_DIRS - the GLIB2 include directory
#  GLIB2_LIBRARIES - Link these to use GLIB2
#  GLIB2_DEFINITIONS - Compiler switches required for using GLIB2
